Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko kuba abana batageze ku myaka itanu barakaraba, bishobora gutuma barushaho kugira amajyambere make.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y’amajyambere, umubare w’abapfa bakiri bato bazira indwara zo guhumeka n’iz’iciro, ushobora kugabanuka binyuriye mu kugira ihinduka ryoroheje mu myifatire, urugero nko gukaraba amaboko ukoresheje isabuni.
Icyo gikorwa cyoroheje gishobora kugabanya umubare w’abantu bapfa bazira izo ndwara ku bantu bagera hafi kuri 50 ku ijana.
Ibintu bituma umuntu yoza ibiganza bishobora kugabanya imisatsi mu buryo bugera hafi kuri kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo bigereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu duce duhembwamo amafaranga make.
Ku ijana by’imyanya y’iby’iciro, bishobora kuba bifitanye isano no gukaraba amaboko n’isabune, ni uburyo bumwe bugira ingaruka nziza kandi butazimvye bwo kwirinda indwara z’iciro n’indwara zikaze ziterwa no guhumeka (ARI), nk’uko imyifatire isanzwe ikorerwa mu ngo, mu mashuri n’imiryango yo hirya no hino ku isi.
Pneumonia, akaba ari umuyobozi mukuru wa ARI, ni yo mpamvu y’ibanze ituma abana badafite imyaka itanu bapfa, ikaba ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1,8 buri mwaka.
Ku mwaka, abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3,5 bapfa bahitanywe n’indwara y’imibembe hamwe n’indwara y’umusonga.
